<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>회원가입</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
{{> layout/navbar}}
<div class="common-middle-box text-center loginscreen animated fadeInDown">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
        <img src="/img/test.png" style="width: 250px; height: 250px;">
    </div>
    <h3>Register to WC</h3>
    <p>이메일 주소만으로 간단히 계정 생성이 가능합니다.</p>
    <form role="form" id="form1">
        <div class="form-group mb-3">
            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="닉네임" required="" id="user_nickname">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group mb-3">
            <input type="email" class="form-control" placeholder="이메일" required="" id="user_email">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group mb-3">
            <input type="password" class="form-control" placeholder="비밀번호" required="" id="user_password">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group mb-3">
            <input type="password" class="form-control" placeholder="비밀번호 확인" required="" id="user_password_check">
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn block w-100 mb-2 common-color-primary common-none-outline-button text-white"
                id="login">계정 생성
        </button>
        <div id="message mb-3"></div>
    </form>
</div>


</body>

</html>